title: Refrigerator Freezer Door Gasket - Gray
description: Refrigerator Freezer Door Gasket - Gray ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 10 Reviews PartSelect Number PS11704172 Manufacturer Part Number 5304501270 This door gasket is for the freezer door on the refrigerator. The gasket is grey in color. This part is approximately 34-1/2" wide x 24" long. The door gasket is on the inner door panel and creates a seal around the door to prevent warm air from entering the freezer compartment.
